
===============================================================================

             Keyboard Overview for TORNADO by Digital Integration

                                (Amiga Version)

===============================================================================


1. Main Controls

   Up                                      NUM 2 or CURSOR DOWN
   Down                                    NUM 8 or CURSOR UP
   Roll Left                               NUM 4 or CURSOR LEFT
   Roll Right                              NUM 6 or CURSOR RIGHT
   Rudder Left                             NUM 0 or LCOMMAND
   Rudder Right                            NUM . or RCOMMAND
   Fine Adjust                             ALT + Keys


2. Thrust Controls

   Increase Thrust/Afterburner             NUM +
   Decrease Thrust/Afterburner             NUM -
   Maximum Thrust/Afterburner On           SHIFT NUM +
   Minimum Thrust/Afterburner Off          SHIFT NUM -


3. Flight Controls

   Sweep Wing Backward 1 Step              S
   Sweep Wing Forward  1 Step              W
   Flaps Down 1 Step                       A
   Flaps Up   1 Step                       Q
   Airbrake                                BACKSPACE
   Reverse Thrust (when landed)            BACKSPACE
   Gear Brakes On/Off                      B
   Gear Up/Down                            G or U
   Jettison
                    external Tanks         ALT   J
                    external Loads         CTRL  J
                    all Loads and Tanks    SHIFT J
   SPILS On/Off                            CTRL  I
   Eject                                   CTRL  E


4. Weapon Controls

   Unlock Air-Ground Weapons               RETURN
   Unlock Air-Air Weapons                  ALT RETURN
   Lock Weapons                            CTRL RETURN
   Select Air-Ground Weapon                K
   Select Air-Ground Targeting Mode        L
   Select Air-Air Weapon                   ; (Ö)
   Fire Weapon                             SPACE
   Release Chaff                           C
   Release Flare                           F
   ECM On/Off                              E


5. Autopilot Controls

   Course to Left                          NUM 4 or CURSOR LEFT
   Course to Right                         NUM 6 or CURSOR RIGHT
   Increase Altitude                       NUM 2 or CURSOR DOWN
   Decrease Altitude                       NUM 8 or CURSOR UP
   Increase ATS Thrust                     NUM +
   Decrease ATS Thrust                     NUM -
   Fine Adjust                             ALT + Keys
   Automatic Trim                          NUM 5
   Approach Mode                           F6
   Track Mode                              F7
   Standard Mode                           F8
   TRN Mode                                F9
   IAS Mode                                F10
   Disable Autopilot                       ESC
   Next Waypoint                           N
   Define Target Waypoint                  T
   Delete Target Waypoint                  CTRL T


6. Cockpit Controls

   HUD Contrast                            H
   HUD On/Off                              CTRL H
   Speed KTS/MACH                          ALT  H
   Radar
         Ground Radar On                   R
         Air Radar On                      ALT  R
         Radar Off                         CTRL R
   Alarm Off                               NUM *
   Toggle Active Window (Mouse)            TAB
   MFD Mode Toggle                         D
   MFD Off                                 CTRL D
   Tactical Map MFD
                    Zoom In/Out            , or .
                    Toggle Centering       O
   Ground Radar MFD
                    Target Select Movement (MOUSE)
                    Select                 LEFT BUTTON
                    Deselect               RIGHT BUTTON
                    Increase Range         CTRL LEFT BUTTON
                    Decrease Range         CTRL RIGHT BUTTON
   Air Radar MFD
                    Target Select Movement (MOUSE)
                    Select Target          LEFT BUTTON
                    Next Target            ALT CAPSLOCK
                    Front Target           CAPSLOCK
                    Forget Target          CTRL CAPSLOCK
                    Increase Range         CTRL LEFT BUTTON
                    Decrease Range         CTRL RIGHT BUTTON
   Toggle Left  TAB Display                [ (Ü)
   Toggle Right TAB Display                ] (+)
   Left  TAB Display On/Off                CTRL [ (CTRL Ü)
   Right TAB Dosplay On/Off                CTRL ] (CTRL +)
   Tactical Map TAB
                    Zoom In/Out            , or .
                    Toggle Centering       O
   TIALD TAB
                    Move TIALD Camera      (MOUSE)
                    Select Target          LEFT BUTTON
                    Deselect Target        RIGHT BUTTON
                    Zoom In                CTRL MOUSE FORWARD
                    Zoom Out               CTRL MOUSE BACKWARD
   Main Map TAB
                    Move Map               (MOUSE)
                    Select Target          LEFT BUTTON
                    Deselect Target        RIGHT BUTTON
                    Zoom In                CTRL LEFT BUTTON
                    Zoom Out               CTRL RIGHT BUTTON
                    Show Plane             ALT LEFT BUTTON
                    Show Target            ALT RIGHT BUTTON
   Overview Map
                    Switch to Map          M
                    Zoom In/Out            , or .


7. Cockpit View Controls

   Select/Toggle Front Seat                CTRL CURSOR UP     or NUM 7
   Select Back Seat                        CTRL CURSOR DOWN   or NUM 9
   Temporary View Left                     CTRL CURSOR LEFT   or NUM 1
   Temporary View Right                    CTRL CURSOR RIGHT  or NUM 3
   View Left                               SHIFT CURSOR LEFT  or SHIFT NUM 1
   View Right                              SHIFT CURSOR RIGHT or SHIFT NUM 3
   View Down (Preferences)                 ~ or NUM [


8. Outside Views

   Track Mode
                    Select                 F1
                    Toggle High/Low        F1
                    Reset                  CTRL F1
   Satelite View
                    Select                 F2
                    Toggle High/Low        F2
                    Reset                  CTRL F2
   Follow View      Select                 F3
   Spectator View
                    Select                 F4
                    Reset                  CTRL F4
   Drone View
                    Select                 F5
                    Next Drone             F5
                    Previous Drone         SHIFT F5
                    Toggle Air/Ground      CTRL F5
                    Toggle Friend/Enemy    ALT F5
   Weapon View
                    Select                 V
                    Reset                  CTRL V

   All Modes
                    Turn Left/Right        Z or X (Y or X)
                    Turn Far Left/Right    SHIFT Z or SHIFT X (SHIFT Y/SHIFT X)
                    Zoom In/Out            , or .
                    Fast Zoom In/Out       SHIFT , or SHIFT .


9. Konfiguration Controls

   Visibility                              1
   Ground Textures                         2
   Hill Textures                           3
   Sky Textures                            4
   Ironwork                                5
   Control Device                          6
   Sound Effects                           7
   Minimize/Restore                        0


10.Other Controls

   End Mission                             CTRL Q
   Pause On/Off                            P


